[Allow Player Profile Names With "inappropriate language"]
author=47iscool
description=Allows you to use politically incorrect names/words that (((THQ))) didn't want you to.
Basically it's the same as the code I made for WWE All-Stars Wii.
A list of the offending/blacklisted words can be found in a RAM dump of this game.
Only use when creating a new profile, otherwise it'll freeze when trying to race. 
patch=1,EE,2041EB08,extended,24020000

[Alternate (& Working) Idiot A.I. L3 On/R3 Off]
author=47iscool
description=The code made by the CodeBreaker team does not work for me.
Only enable right at the race start when the announcer says "1".
If enabled before that, or in menus the camera will act VERY screwy.
Also it's not perfect, but it's the best I can do for now.
patch=1,EE,D05241C2,extended,0000FFFD
patch=1,EE,20419648,extended,00000000
patch=1,EE,D05241C2,extended,0000FFFB
patch=1,EE,20419648,extended,44026000

[Always Win Drift Event]
author=47iscool
description=Gives about 17 million plus points at the end of the race.
